extracted_text: Such uses shall not be nearer than 200 feet to a lot not in the same zoning district classification (RA-40) or other use not located within the same planned development.
llm_outputs.rationale: The text mentions a 200 feet requirement for stables or corrals in the RA-40 zoning district. However, this is not referring to a minimum unit size, but rather a setback requirement from other zoning districts or uses. There is no specific information about the minimum unit size for residential units in the RA-40 district.
